35:33.265 --> 35:36.735
**

35:39.305 --> 35:40.972
DR. MELENDEZ:
Welcome back, Hunter.

35:41.039 --> 35:42.073
(GROANS)

35:42.140 --> 35:45.043
The mass was tightly adhered
in some spots,

35:45.110 --> 35:49.348
so we're not exactly sure
what to expect moving forward.
But the cord looked healthy.

35:49.415 --> 35:51.683
We're gonna be bringing in
several specialists
to work with you.

35:51.750 --> 35:53.719
The first will be
a neurophysiatrist...

35:53.785 --> 35:55.721
Thank you.
Thank you.

35:55.787 --> 35:57.989
Thank you.
I'm grateful to all of you.

35:58.056 --> 36:01.260
Would you mind if we talked
about the rest of this later?

36:02.361 --> 36:04.296
I just want to
sit with my wife.

36:08.634 --> 36:10.436
Thank you.

36:11.970 --> 36:14.273
Hey. Hey. Hey.

36:14.340 --> 36:17.309
**

36:21.813 --> 36:23.249
(SNIFFLES)

36:23.315 --> 36:24.816
(SNIFFLES)

36:27.152 --> 36:28.520
(GROANS)

36:29.321 --> 36:32.524
**

36:49.007 --> 36:51.510
I met a couple today
that lost their way.

36:54.513 --> 36:56.282
They loved each other,

36:59.117 --> 37:01.052
but by the time
they remembered
what really mattered,

37:01.119 --> 37:02.388
it was too late.

37:07.158 --> 37:10.128
I don't want us
to be like them.

37:10.195 --> 37:13.231
I want to be
fully committed to you.

37:15.667 --> 37:17.168
I love you, too.

37:19.438 --> 37:20.872
(CHUCKLES)

37:25.744 --> 37:28.847
There's a surgery I could have
that should make me fertile,

37:28.914 --> 37:30.716
but there's a risk
of impotency.

37:35.020 --> 37:36.722
What do you want to do?

37:36.788 --> 37:38.089
I want to give you
what you want,

37:38.156 --> 37:39.425
what we want,
a family.

37:41.192 --> 37:42.861
We are a family.

37:43.862 --> 37:46.131
Yes, I want children,

37:46.197 --> 37:48.300
and there are many ways
to do that,

37:48.367 --> 37:51.002
which we'll explore
together.

37:51.069 --> 37:54.072
But I draw the line
at anything
that risks our sex life.

37:54.940 --> 37:57.743
**

38:05.116 --> 38:06.685
It's just
one night a week,

38:06.752 --> 38:09.555
but I think this could be
my big break, you know?

38:09.621 --> 38:10.956
Well, you always had
a beautiful voice.

38:12.123 --> 38:15.026
Well, everyone's
got one thing, right?

38:15.093 --> 38:17.429
But enough about me.
I want to hear about you.

38:18.296 --> 38:19.465
Do you have a man?

38:20.231 --> 38:22.167
I did.

38:22.233 --> 38:26.004
Pretty young thing
should have plenty of choices.

38:26.071 --> 38:27.939
Hmm, I'm not looking to
complicate my life right now.

38:28.774 --> 38:30.008
Hmm.

38:30.075 --> 38:33.745
Still looking after
everyone else but yourself,

38:33.812 --> 38:35.547
like you did for me.

38:37.649 --> 38:40.586
* Set your dreams
where nobody hides

38:40.652 --> 38:43.021
You know,
I know brag to everyone.

38:43.088 --> 38:44.890
"My baby.
She's a surgeon."

38:44.956 --> 38:46.692
Surgical resident.

38:46.758 --> 38:47.826
Right, sorry.

38:49.094 --> 38:50.396
You like it?

38:52.864 --> 38:54.766
I love it.

38:54.833 --> 38:58.169
* Give your tears to the tide

38:58.236 --> 39:00.506
Where are you staying?
You're...
Are you in town for a while?

39:00.572 --> 39:02.508
Yeah.

39:02.574 --> 39:04.109
I'd like
to be closer to you.

39:04.843 --> 39:07.446
**

39:08.614 --> 39:10.616
I found a place.

39:11.983 --> 39:13.585
You'd like it,

39:13.652 --> 39:17.188
but I just need to put up
first and last.

39:17.255 --> 39:19.425
* No time

39:20.626 --> 39:21.893
I'll pay you back.

39:22.728 --> 39:24.963
**

39:27.165 --> 39:28.567
How much do you need?

39:28.634 --> 39:30.536
$2,500.

39:30.602 --> 39:33.539
Plus I have to get furniture
and, you know, all of that.

39:33.605 --> 39:35.373
I thought maybe you could
help me pick that stuff out.

39:35.441 --> 39:36.675
You've always been
so good at that.

39:36.742 --> 39:38.444
I really appreciate it.
I'm good for it.

39:39.344 --> 39:41.713
**

39:45.316 --> 39:47.252
(SIREN WAILS)

39:47.318 --> 39:50.722
**

40:06.371 --> 40:09.841
* Set your dreams
where nobody hides

40:09.908 --> 40:12.711
KENNY:
Uh, Celeste isn't coming.
She broke up with me.

40:12.778 --> 40:15.146
I hate her.

40:15.213 --> 40:18.517
But I'm not gonna let that
ruin our night.

40:18.584 --> 40:19.885
That's what friends are for.

40:19.951 --> 40:22.488
They got each other's backs,
rain or shine.

40:22.554 --> 40:25.757
By the by, I found a $20
in your battery drawer,

40:25.824 --> 40:27.425
so I got us
Chinese food.

40:27.493 --> 40:30.496
Don't thank me.
I don't like Chinese food.

40:30.562 --> 40:31.830
Aw, come on now.

40:31.897 --> 40:34.600
Trust me, everybody likes
Ma Jong's Kung Pao.

40:34.666 --> 40:38.970
* Set your dreams
where nobody hides

40:39.037 --> 40:40.872
There you go.

40:40.939 --> 40:44.042
I'm pretty torn up
about that Celeste thing.
She was a real keeper.

40:44.109 --> 40:46.011
You said
you hated Celeste.

40:46.077 --> 40:47.713
I do.
I... I hate her 'cause...

40:47.779 --> 40:49.715
I don't know...
I kind of love her.

40:50.916 --> 40:52.484
This tastes terrible.

40:52.551 --> 40:55.253
Okay,
then he hates Chinese food.

40:55.320 --> 40:57.022
More for me.

40:57.088 --> 40:58.323
Plain white rice?

40:59.725 --> 41:01.793
* No time

41:01.860 --> 41:03.495
Oh, uh,
I got a gaming console,

41:03.562 --> 41:05.396
and I hooked it up to
your bad boy over there.

41:05.463 --> 41:06.865
We can play some
Mortal Kombat.

41:06.932 --> 41:09.067
**

41:09.134 --> 41:10.235
Come on.

41:13.171 --> 41:14.906
* No time *

41:14.973 --> 41:17.008
We doing this or what?

41:18.276 --> 41:19.711
It sounds fun.

41:21.613 --> 41:24.716
**

41:24.783 --> 41:26.284
Yeah, there you go.

41:26.351 --> 41:27.719
This one's you.

41:29.955 --> 41:32.357
That's you on the left
right there.

41:32.423 --> 41:34.225
Okay.
Yeah.

41:34.292 --> 41:37.929
You got four arms,
but you're naked,
so here we go.

41:37.996 --> 41:40.365
SHAUN: I gave you
a pneumothorax.

41:40.431 --> 41:42.300
KENNY: Ah, I didn't
realize how bloody
this game was.

41:42.367 --> 41:43.902
Ooh, a fireball.
I got you there.

41:45.103 --> 41:46.437
Have you played
this before?

41:46.504 --> 41:49.741
SHAUN: That looks like
a spinal fracture.

41:49.808 --> 41:51.877
KENNY: Yeah, I'd say...
I'd say there's
a huge fracture there.

41:51.943 --> 41:53.144
SHAUN: You died.

41:56.682 --> 41:59.685
**
